title: Finding Your Potential
itunes:title: Finding Your Potential
description:
Episode 598 - What would your life look like if you had 3,650 perfect days in a row? See, we all have moments in our lives where we feel like we are living up to our potential but a lot of the time we feel like we are not. We feel like there is more that we can do. We feel like there is more that we could bring to the world. In this episode, I will teach you how to bring out the potential that you have hiding inside of yourself! If you are ready to break out of your comfort zones, join my Iron Mind 60 challenge at www.IronMind60.com
